<div id="pageheader">
	<h2><a class="titles" href="./viewtopic.php?f=22&amp;t=13872">Long-term goal: a Metal Gear-like game for NES</a></h2>


	<p class="moderators">Moderator: <a href="./memberlist.php?mode=group&amp;g=320">Moderators</a></p>

</div>

